Rory McIlroy battled with Fifty Shades of Grey star Jamie Dornan to promote new football concept Circular Soccer . 
  The World No 1 golfer won 2-1 in the first game of the 2015 season . 
  The game is based on a three sided goal and aims to improve skill and ball control . 
  McIlory was taking part in the game to promote the new concept . 
  The golfer was taking time off after the Masters in Augusta . 
 